            "id": 6098544,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 中傑-KY(6965)急拉3.94%報106.0元，成交199張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中傑-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6965:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6965\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6965-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.94%，08日12:49報106.0元，成交199張，今日漲幅為0％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中傑-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6965:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6965\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6965-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.85%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-33 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-34 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+1 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6098544",
